'''聖克里斯多福及尼維斯駐外機構列表'''列出了[[聖克里斯多福及尼維斯|聖克里斯多福及尼維斯]]在各國的[[外交代表機構|外交代表機構]]，包含[[大使館|大使館]]、[[領事館|領事館]]、[[高級專員|高級專員]]公署、代表團等。位於[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]的聖克里斯多福及尼維斯僅有少量的駐外機構，與其他[[東加勒比國家組織|東加勒比國家組織]]成員國共享位於[[布鲁塞尔-首都大区|布鲁塞尔]]的駐[[歐洲聯盟|歐盟]]代表團<ref name="OECS Brussels">{{cite web|title=Brussels Mission|url=https://pressroom.oecs.org/category/brussels-mission|publisher=Organisation of Eastern Caribbean States|accessdate=2020-09-26|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801184640/https://pressroom.oecs.org/category/brussels-mission|dead-url=no}}</ref>、駐[[日內瓦|日內瓦]]技術代表團<ref>{{cite web|title=The OECS Technical Mission in Geneva|url=https://www.oecs.org/our-work/overseas/geneva|publisher=Organisation of Eastern Caribbean States|accessdate=2020-09-26|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926174922/https://www.oecs.org/our-work/overseas/geneva|dead-url=no}}</ref>、以及駐[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]大使館<ref>{{cite web|title=The Embassies of the Eastern Caribbean States to the Kingdom of Morocco|publisher=Organisation of Eastern Caribbean States|url=https://oecs.org/embassies-of-eastern-caribbean-states-morocco|accessdate=2020-09-26|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926174922/https://oecs.org/embassies-of-eastern-caribbean-states-morocco|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該國承認[[中華民國|中華民國]]，並於[[臺北市|臺北市]]設有大使館。

